# Lesson 01 Livebook: Linear Time

The protocol starts in calm water.

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:wormhole_protocol, path: "../01_linear_time"}
])
```

## Run The Baseline Timeline

```elixir
story = WormholeProtocol.linear_story!()

%{
  available_oxygen: story.available_oxygen,
  allocations: story.allocations,
  facts: Enum.map(story.facts, & &1.event.__struct__)
}
```

## Inspect The Accepted Sector State

```elixir
story.sector
```
